    "description": "a web server to investigate the effect of DNA methylation-related functional elements on prognosis.\n\nThe functional elements associated with DNA methylation, for example enhancer region, CpG island, shore, shelf, promoter, gene body, etc., are discovered to be underlying prognostic markers for patients' survival.Here, we built a web server SurvivalMeth (freely available via a user friendly web-server at http://bio-bigdata.hrbmu.edu.cn/survivalmeth/) to investigate the effect of DNA methylation-related functional elements on prognosis, and multiple kinds of commonly used functional elements associated with DNA methylation are considered.",
